worked_examples:
'if/else': Check if a user is logged in.
is_logged_in = False
if is_logged_in:
    print("Welcome back!")
else:
    print("Please log in.")

'if/elif/else': Assign a grade based on a score.
score = 85
if score >= 90:
    print("Grade A")
elif score >= 80:
    print("Grade B")
else:
    print("Grade C")

